name: 11906-BKHP-LACE UP-SS16
description:
Casual, comfortable style achieves a new level with the SKECHERS Relaxed Fit: Sorino - Evole shoe. Smooth soft pigskin nubuck and suede upper in a lace up casual comfort sneaker oxford with stitching and overlay accents. Memory Foam insole.

Construction

  • Smooth soft pigskin nubuck leather upper
  • Soft suede overlays at sides and heel
  • Fabric and synthetic detailing
  • Lace up casual sporty comfort sneaker oxford design
  • Stitching accents
  • Side and heel overlay detail
  • Side panels feature contrast colored buck stitching and fabric stripe detail
  • Embossed S logo on heel panel
  • SKECHERS logo label on side panel
  • Lace up front with metal eyelets
  • Padded collar and tongue
  • Soft fabric shoe lining
  • Relaxed Fit design for a roomy comfortable fit
  • Memory Foam cushioned comfort insole
  • Shock absorbing midsole
  • Flexible rubber traction outsole
